task.summary: Tilemap can now be generated by 2D-Array
Added rotation and game is now centered
Optimized npm scripts for tool chain
Refactored: Tiledata is now cascaded from 'game' to <Tile/> as data attribute
Added algorithm for updating state of tilemap
Functionality to rotate tiles and update tilemap evaluation
Added generator to generate playable tilemaps (WIP)
Solving the puzzles generates a new one
Made game responsive on different tilemap sizes
Added delay after completing a stage
